modShortDescription: This mod removes the demolitioner zombies from the 7 Days to Die. Once and for all. Community is really annoyed of this entity. Understandable. So removed.
modDescription:
This mod removes the demolitioner [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) from the 7 Days to Die. Once and for all. A quick mod, done for Killerlady12, because the community is really annoyed of this entity. Understandable. So removed.

Compatibility: A18+

[Download](https://www.mediafire.com/file/tvt24uw2hpzvmrx/Claymore_No_Demolitioners.zip)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/15031-claymores-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Claymore](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/claymore/)
